title: [Norigorou] Imaizumi Brings All The Gyarus To His House
description: Some gyarus have decided to use Imaizumi's house as a gathering spot to play video games and eat snacks. When Reina gets bored with video games, she sets her sights on another toy in the house: Imaizumi himself...
author: Norigorou

6.2.title: A Day with Reina and Yukina
